headline: EA SPORTS™ NHL® 26 Elevates Authenticity With NHL EDGE Partnership and ICE-Q 2.0 Integration
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., August 11, 2025--Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) today announced a groundbreaking new partnership with the National Hockey League to integrate official NHL EDGE data directly into EA SPORTS™ NHL® 26, marking a new era for authenticity in sports gaming and entertainment. This collaboration brings the same advanced analytics used by NHL teams into the hands of players and fans, powering the all-new ICE-Q 2.0 gameplay system for the most realistic hockey gameplay ever.
